 blowouts, pruning, and weed control.</p><span class="cs-related-arrow" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></span></a></li><li class="cs-related-card"><a href="/services/landscaping/xeriscaping/" class="cs-related-link"><h3 class="cs-related-title">Xeriscaping</h3><p class="cs-related-text">Convert thirsty lawn to a drip-irrigated xeriscape and stop fighting the system.</p><span class="cs-related-arrow" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75"><path d="M4 12 L12 4"></path><path d="M6 4 L12 4 L12 10"></path></svg></span></a></li></ul></div></section><section id="lets-talk-318"><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/talk-tree.svg" height="457" width="427" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-tree"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/talk-bird-1.svg" height="20" width="64" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-bird cs-bird-1"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/talk-bird-2.svg" height="15" width="56" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-bird cs-bird-2"> <img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/talk-bird-3.svg" height="15" width="46" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-bird cs-bird-3"><div class="cs-container"><h2 class="cs-title">Ready to Stop Fighting Your Sprinklers?</h2><a href="/contact/" class="cs-talk-button">Schedule a Diagnosis</a></div><img alt="" decoding="async" src="/assets/svgs/talk-grass-top.svg" aria-hidden="true" class="cs-grass"></section>
